{"tid":2443563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國政府施壓後  Facebook撤回加州至香港光纖電纜","createTime":"2021-03-12T06:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T06:59:57.000Z","uid":227801,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"04572ad72141a219a9e0b3c32d267b78b3eff3cc","tid":2443563,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=427002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427002&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=96441ac1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427002&h=30ca74a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=427002</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】Facebook撤回在美國加州與香港之間，建設海底光纖電纜的申請。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook發言人在聲明中表示，由於美國政府持續對美國與香港之間，有直接通訊連繫感到擔憂，所以向聯邦通訊委員會取消這項稱為「HKA」光纖電纜項目的申請；公司期待與各方合作重新配置系統，以釋除華府的疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，美國國家安全官員認為，港區國安法實施容許執法機構監管網絡，憂慮美國的網絡受威脅，因此向Facebook施壓，要求撤銷光纖電纜申請。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook與多間電訊業夥伴，2018年首次就這項計劃提出申請，建設分別連接至香港與台灣的海底光纖電纜。"},{"pid":"9bcfa4c9e530237de77fa4ec89c249013291ba99","tid":2443563,"uid":180302,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:42:34.000Z","msg":"轉做駁去台灣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfce6d6701ab92a6a028538ae053bdc7ccdde865","tid":2443563,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682da5fa867ab45271c9ef51980e481c94593308","tid":2443563,"uid":311611,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"香港以後上唔到美國網. gamestop 都block 9 佢香港."},{"pid":"7c16313734f2671ff733c93f9c